tivated complications that have bedeviled the systematic coverage of the orthographic system and its acquisition. These have had a detrimental effect on systematic spelling instruction, and various articles take a closer look at them.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aGerman languagexOrthography and spellingvCongresses. 0aGerman languagexOrthography and spellingxStudy and teaching (Elementary)vCongresses. 0aGerman languagexStudy and teaching (Elementary)vCongresses. 0aReading (Elementary)vCongresses. 4aAufsatzsammlung. 4aDeutsch. 4aRechtschreibung. 4aRechtschreibunterricht. 4aSpracherwerb. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh1 aBredel, Ursula, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBredel, Ursula, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aFuhrhop, Nanna, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGeilfuß-Wolfgang, Jochen, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGünther, Hartmut, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGünther, Hartmut, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aIsele, Inga, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aNoack, Christina, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPrimus, Beatrice, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRisel, Heinz, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRöber, Christa, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Linguistics and Semiotics 2000 - 2014z9783110636970oZDB-23-DLS08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2006z9783110277128oZDB-23-DGG08i